"{\"uid\": \"swissinfo.ch-eng-paris-mayor-wants-russian-athletes-banned-from-olympics-73698049\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Follow us  PARIS (Reuters) -     Paris mayor Anne Hidalgo on Wednesday said she hoped Russian athletes would be banned from taking part in the Paris Olympics and their opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18, \"end\": 25, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.784524567916007e-12, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 33, \"end\": 38, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999939163899, \"rank\": 6.083522287120745e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 45, \"end\": 57, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}, {\"begin\": 86, \"end\": 93, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.8644225861726826, \"rank\": 0.13855796482546814, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Israeli athletes, however, should be fully welcome, she told Reuters in an interview, as organisers of the July 26-Aug. 11 Games prepare to deal with issues arising from the wars in Ukraine and Gaza.\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 187, \"end\": 194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.8052832641964169, \"rank\": 0.214459355641943, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 248, \"end\": 255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.784524567916007e-12, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 369, \"end\": 376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999719788180927, \"rank\": 2.7889644658496158e-05, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 381, \"end\": 385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 0.99577139432385, \"rank\": 0.00424656271503553, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee, which decides on such matters, is due to discuss at a next session the question of the participation of Russian and Belarusian athletes in the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 392, \"end\": 423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 529, \"end\": 536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.8644225861726826, \"rank\": 0.13855796482546814, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 541, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"score\": 0.9995854450808874, \"rank\": 0.00020407780114683796, \"text\": \"Belarusian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For now, Russian and Belarusian athletes cannot take part under their countries' flag, but are allowed to participate as neutrals - without flags or anthems being played.\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 596, \"end\": 603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.8644225861726826, \"rank\": 0.13855796482546814, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 608, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"score\": 0.9995854450808874, \"rank\": 0.00020407780114683796, \"text\": \"Belarusian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I prefer that they do not come,\\\" Hidalgo said in an interview with Reuters.\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 793, \"end\": 800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9999994055030532, \"rank\": 4.7557139676609085e-07, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}, {\"begin\": 827, \"end\": 834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.784524567916007e-12, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Paralympic Committee (IPC) said last week that Russian and Belarusian athletes joining the Paralympics would not be part of their opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 1002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 841, \"end\": 881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Paralympic Committee (IPC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 841, \"end\": 881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Paralympic Committee (IPC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.8644225861726826, \"rank\": 0.13855796482546814, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 914, \"end\": 924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"score\": 0.9995854450808874, \"rank\": 0.00020407780114683796, \"text\": \"Belarusian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We cannot act as if (Russia's invasion of Ukraine) did not exist,\\\" the Socialist mayor said.\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1026, \"end\": 1032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999740331274506, \"rank\": 2.5538309731607256e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999719788180927, \"rank\": 2.7889644658496158e-05, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We could not act as if (Vladimir) Putin was not a dictator who today threatens the whole of Europe.\\\"\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1133, \"end\": 1138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1065601523591418e-17, \"text\": \"Putin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked about Israel's participation in the Olympics, while the war in Gaza is raging following the Oct. 7 attack by Hamas, Hidalgo said there was no comparison with Russia.\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1213, \"end\": 1219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9999999996932729, \"rank\": 1.5378245434524737e-10, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 1270, \"end\": 1274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 0.99577139432385, \"rank\": 0.00424656271503553, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}, {\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 0.99999999851957, \"rank\": 1.4804262622812846e-09, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7